		"name": "Aurora Hotel Management System - API Tests",
		"description": "Comprehensive API Testing Collection for Aurora Hotel System\n\n## Test Flow\n1. **Authentication** - Login and get tokens\n2. **User Management** - Register and manage users\n3. **Branch Management** - Create and manage hotel branches\n4. **Amenity Management** - Manage hotel amenities (WiFi, TV, etc.)\n5. **Facility Management** - Manage branch facilities (Pool, Gym, Spa)\n6. **Room Type Management** - Configure room types\n7. **Room Management** - Manage individual rooms\n8. **Service Management** - Hotel services (Laundry, Room service, etc.)\n9. **Promotion Management** - Discounts and promotions\n10. **Booking Management** - Room bookings\n11. **Booking Room** - Booking-Room relationship\n12. **Service Booking** - Service bookings for guests\n13. **Payment Management** - Process payments\n14. **Role & Permission** - Manage access control\n\n## Authentication\nAll endpoints (except register and login) require Bearer token authentication.\n\n## Default Users\n- **Admin**: username=`admin`, password=`Admin@123`\n- **Manager**: username=`manager`, password=`Manager@123`\n- **Staff**: username=`staff`, password=`Staff@123`\n- **Customer**: username=`customer`, password=`Customer@123`",
